      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELLE GEM (8) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Finished in the minors last time when third (29.36) at this track making it back to back placings. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Deserves serious consideration. AUDACIOUS PADDY (4) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 2.75 lengths into second (26.19) at Warragul in a Rank Limit - Grade 5 over 460m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Overdue and is among the main hopes. JUMBUK WANG WANG (2) was a little disappointing last start at Healesville when 7th (19.88) over 350m. Has never missed the frame here at the trip including one win. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. SPICY VIKING (5) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
